charges.charge_description: 18:922G.F UNLAWFUL TRANSPORT OF FIREARMS, ETC.; possession of firearms by convicted felon and firearm had previously been transported in interstate commerce(1)

charges.charge_disposition: RESENTENCED TO TIME SERVED AND 3 YEARS SUPERVISED RELEASE ON 9/16/16 - Deft. sent. to BOP for a term of impr. of 262 mos., as to ct. one 262 mos., as to cts. two and three 120 mos. as to each ct. to run concurrenctly with ct. 1 and with each other; 5 yrs. s/rls as to ct. 1 and as to cts. 2 &; 3, 3 yrs to run concurrently with ct. one and with each other with special conditions as noted; $150.00 SMA and restitution in the amount of $175.00 payable to Lawrence Stanley.
